ssues will be highlighted, several top experts on climate science in the country have also been invited to offer their insights on the issues. In particular, one of the primary challenges is to build human capacity in Earth System Modeling (ESM) in the country - which is essential for providing reliable scientific inputs for policy and decision making on climate change issues.\u000a\u000a... contd.\u000a\u000aALSO READ Jan 31 deadline looms, those without Aadhaar ID will have to pay market price for LPG\u000a\u000aPlease read our terms of use before posting comments
